                "actions": {
                    "value": "2"
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The animated furnace opens its door and fans its flames in a 30-foot cone that deals [[/r 5d6 #fire]] fire damage (<span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Fan the Flames DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>"
